1\ install ruby installer
2\ install rubygems
3\ run command in cmd window
    gem install jekyll
4\ make dir and create jekyll blog, then run jekyll server
    (1) mkdir XXX(Jekyll blog dir)
    (2) jekyll new YYY(blog name)
    (3) cd XXX
    (4) jekyll server(if pop error tip, try "bundle exec jekyll server")
    (5) http://127.0.0.1:4000/